'''Idrarn n Waṭlas''' (s [[tifinaɣ]]: '''ⵉⴷⵓⵔⴰⵔ ⵏ ⵡⴰⵟⵍⴰⵙ''') gan yat trabbut imqqurn n [[Adrar|idrarn]] illan ɣ [[Tafriqt n ugafa|tfriqt n ugafa]]. Idrarn ad umẓn zɣ iffus utrim n [[Lmɣrib]] ar ugafa n [[Tuns]]. Gisn ar nttafa udrar n [[Adrar n Tubqal|Tubqal]] lli igan adrar akkʷ iɣzzifn ɣ ammas n [[Tamazɣa|tmazɣa]] s yat tiɣzi ilkmn uggar n 4100m.

Idurar n waṭlas gant yan mnnaw n idrarn , ar tn nttafa ɣ ugafa utrim n umnẓaw n [[Tafriqt|Tfriqt]] ɣ tmizar n [[Tuns]] d [[Dzayr]] d [[Lmɣrib]] s tiɣzi n 2500 km (1600 Mill), afa yakk iɣzzifn n idrarn ad igatt adrar n [[Tubqal]] (Tugg kal) illan ɣ ammas n unẓul utrim n Tgldit n [[lmɣrib]] s waddud itlkamn ar 4167 m, [[Ill Agrakal|yill agrakal]] ad iḥuddan idrarn n Waṭlas zɣ ugafa, zɣ yiffus tettals-it-d tanẓruft imqqurn, zɣ utaram Agaraw anaṭlas.

